graph TB
    subgraph "Notebook Controller"
        Controller[NotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        Culler[CullingReconciler<br/>Idle Notebook Monitor]
        Metrics[Metrics Collector<br/>Prometheus Exporter]
        VirtualServiceMgr[VirtualService Manager<br/>Istio Integration]

        Controller -->|monitors| Culler
        Controller -->|emits| Metrics
        Controller -->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualServiceMgr
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        NotebookV1[Notebook CR v1<br/>Storage Version]
        NotebookV1Beta1[Notebook CR v1beta1<br/>Webhook Support]
        NotebookV1Alpha1[Notebook CR v1alpha1<br/>Legacy Version]

        NotebookV1Alpha1 -.->|conversion| NotebookV1Beta1
        NotebookV1Beta1 -.->|conversion| NotebookV1
    end

    subgraph "Kubernetes Resources Created"
        StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Pod Instance]
        Service[Service<br/>Port 80→8888]
        VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>Istio Routing]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>networking.istio.io/v1alpha3]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI/API]
        NotebookImages[Notebook Images<br/>Container Registry]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>Sidecar Auth]
        Profiles[Kubeflow Profiles<br/>Multi-tenancy]
    end

    %% User interactions
    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates via| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookV1

    %% Controller watches and creates resources
    NotebookV1 -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|creates/manages| StatefulSet
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Service
    Controller -->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualService

    %% Dependencies
    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    VirtualServiceMgr -->|creates| Istio
    Metrics -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus

    %% Culler queries notebook services
    Culler -->|queries /api/kernels, /api/terminals| Service

    %% Notebook uses images and auth
    StatefulSet -->|pulls| NotebookImages
    StatefulSet -.->|optional sidecar| OAuthProxy

    %% Kubeflow variant
    NotebookV1 -.->|when in Kubeflow mode| Profiles

